  <num>7-858.07</num>
  <heading>Penalties.</heading>
  <text>Civil fines and penalties may be imposed as sanctions for an infraction of <cite path="§7-858.02|(a)">§ 7-858.02(a)</cite> or <cite path="§7-858.02|(c)">(c)</cite>, <cite path="§7-858.03|(a)">§ 7-858.03(a)</cite>, or <cite path="§7-858.04|(a)">§ 7-858.04(a)</cite> pursuant to <cite path="2|18">Chapter 18 of Title 2</cite> ("Civil Infractions Act"). Enforcement and adjudication of an infraction shall be pursuant to the Civil Infractions Act.</text>
